This DIRECTORY is an Annual Supplement to THE BREWERS’ JOURNAL, New York; subscription,

CHANGES IN FIRM NAMES and NEW BREWERIES are published monthly in

Brewers of Lager Beer, Ale and Porter or Weiss

Beer are designated by capital letters, as follows:

: Lager Beer, L; Ale and Porter, A; Weiss Beer, W.

‘ Brewers who are also bottlers are designated by the capital letter B.

' Brewers who have malt houses and make all or

1 part of the malt used by them are designated by

a star (*).
